This directory contains all include files for the DKB system. Wherever they are included, relative pathnames (e.g. "../include/cosmetic.h") are provided.

Selecting A Destination System
------------------------------

Before compiling any source files, you must select a destination system. 
Currently, two options are provided:

	- Sun Workstations running SunOS, supporting RPCs
	- Standard UNIX installations

Sun Workstations
----------------

Copy the file sun.h into select.h by using the command :
	
	cp sun.h select.h

then edit the file hosts.h to meet the requirements of your installation.

UNIX Systems
------------

Copy the file unix.h into select.h by using the command :
	
	cp unix.h select.h

